    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Finding Comfort</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Bruce Kleinschmidt letter on James C McKinley's August 11 article on sports fan mania notes Liverpool Football Club's song is You'll Never Walk Alone0</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Sports Editor:</p>
        <p>I enjoyed the comments and observations about fan solidarity in James C. McKinley's article. The Liverpool Football Club has a song and it is particularly comforting to hear strains of ''You'll Never Walk Alone'' across the airwaves from England to me.</p>
        <p>BRUCE KLEINSCHMIDT  Indianapolis</p>
      </block>
